                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Secretary of State Acheson held a news conference at the Department of State on
                    June 28, prior to which he delivered some remarks relating to President Truman’s
                    statement of June 27 concerning United States support for the Republic of Korea;
                    for the text of Secretary Acheson’s remarks, see Department of State <hi
                        rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, July 3, 1950, page 6.</p>
            </div>
